data.name: Summer of Loggins
data.description:
This summer, Professor of Rock and Kenny Loggins will team up to tell the story behind some of Kennys greatest hits. Were calling it the Summer of Loggins so stay tuned! Well release a new video each Tuesday afternoon!

To finish off the Summer of Loggins, Professor of Rock will hold a live event on Saturday, October 6th at the beautiful Sand Hollow Resort in St. George, Utah.

Were also on the hunt for Kennys biggest fan. Enter the contest to win free tickets, roundtrip airfare, and accommodations for two on our Facebook fan page.
